title.rendered: BOSS AIR IMPRESSOR INCAB ANALOGUE KIT

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR IMPRESSOR INCAB ANALOGUE KIT

Boss Air Impressor Incab Analogue Kit available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

This kit is an all round air package kit for a 2 airbag system, onboard air for the 4×4 or running air lockers, tyres and small air tools.

Featuring the Boss dual needle 200psi gauge, stainless panel with toggle switch and dump vales, PX06 12volt 1.8cfm 100% Duty Cycle Air Compressor for rapid refilling the 5 port tank ready for the next use. Comes with our light weight, no rust Aluminium 3 gallon air tank, heat treated, shot blasted and anodised.

Includes:

  • 1 x PX-06 12volt 100% Duty, 1.8cfm Air Compressors
  • 1 x AT-03  5 port Boss Aluminium Air Tank
  • 1 x 110-135psi Pressure Switch
  • 1 x Braided Hoses with check Valve
  • 1 x Brass 1/4″ Bung
  • 1 x Drain Tap
  • 1 x 40amp Relay
  • 10 metres J844 DOT certified air line
  • 1 x “Y” Check Valve
  • 2 “Y” connectors
  • 4 “T” connectors
  • 1 x200PSI BOSS Dual Needle Gauge
  • Independent Left & Right “Dump Valves”
  • Polished Aluminium Panel
  • 5 x 1/4″ push fittings
  • Momentary 12v Switch for actuating the Valve
  • Mini 12v Electric Solenoid/Valve
  • 1 x tube sealant
  • Instruction Sheet
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
